Lunarpine calls Shadow Wing over his comm, "Wing, I need a favour, 
get airborn and use your scanners to find Megatrons exaust trail. If 
at all possible find a way to mark it."

Again he tries to push his point across to Ramhorn, "I can track that 
mechan slime slug. He needs to be taught a lesson that we're not just 
his toys." Thoughts go through the wolfs brain of what he'd like to 
teach the tyrant."If I get my paws on him I'll teach him a lesson of 
the permanent kind."
